column2:
"I have my doubts about ARKS. Don't you think
it's messed up that their roles are based purely
on innate ability?"

"僕はアークスに疑問をもっています。
才能だけで定められる職業というのは
なんとも歪だと思いませんか？"

"I have my doubts about ARKS. Don't you think
it's messed up that their roles are based purely
on innate ability?"

"僕はアークスに疑問をもっています。
才能だけで定められる職業というのは
なんとも歪だと思いませんか？"

"How come there are discrepancies in people's ability to handle photons, even if they grow up in
the same environment and conditions?"

"同じ環境、同じ条件で生育してるのに
どうしてフォトンを扱う力に
差が生まれるんでしょう……"

"How come there are discrepancies in people's ability to handle photons, even if they grow up in
the same environment and conditions?"

"同じ環境、同じ条件で生育してるのに
どうしてフォトンを扱う力に
差が生まれるんでしょう……"

"How come there are discrepancies in people's ability to handle Photons, even if they grow up in
the same environment and conditions?"

"同じ環境、同じ条件で生育してるのに
どうしてフォトンを扱う力に
差が生まれるんでしょう……"

"Where does the ability to manipulate photons
come from? I wonder what sort of organ it is......
I've looked this up, but I have no idea. "

"フォトンを扱う力とは何なのか。
それはどういう器官なのか……
調べてもわからないんですよね。"

"I heard there is research on acquired photon abilities. .......I wonder what that is like. "

"後天的なフォトン付与の研究が
行われていると聞きました。
……どのようなものなのでしょう。"
"I heard there is research on acquired photon abilities. .......I wonder what that is like. "

".......I don't know. What on earth is happening? "

"……わかりません。
一体、何がどうなっているんですか？"
